text: Always important to have a public toilet that's accessible, whether smelly or otherwise. It's a functional toilet, deal with it. With all the activities that are happening around here, this isn't going to be a toilet you want to spend your life in. Do what you need to, and get the hell out. At least there's even a toilet, in a nature park.
Small smelly toilet with sinks outside
Good smell, would recommend coming to smell the smells of nature around it. Really makes you feel at home
Pretty ok in terms of cleanliness. Nice location for park-goers.
Sometimes stink but complaints are not made
